research_municipality_step.notes: Woodville, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which is a mayor-council system. One council member position is currently vacant. There was a discrepancy in sources regarding the Mayor Pro Tem, with one source listing Joyce Wilson and another listing Kelly Dillard; Kelly Dillard was chosen based on being listed as both Mayor Pro Tem and a Council Member in a more recent directory. The 'Place' numbers refer to council positions.
